    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a vertical wall of whirling, razor-sharp blades made of magical energy within the spell’s range. You can make a straight wall up to 100 feet long, 20 feet high, and 5 feet thick, or a ringed wall up to 60 feet in diameter, 20 feet high, and 5 feet thick. The wall provides three‑quarters cover to creatures behind it, and its space is difficult terrain.</p><p>When a creature enters the wall’s area for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there, the creature must make a [[/save]] save. On a failure, the creature takes [[/damage]] damage or half as much damage on a success.</p>",
